# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Intent OS — Environment Variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your API keys.
# At least one adapter is needed for execution.
# Ollama works without any API key (local inference).

# ── OpenAI Adapter ──
# Enables: intent-os run <manifest> --adapter openai
# Get key: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# ── Anthropic Adapter ──
# Enables: intent-os run <manifest> --adapter anthropic
# Get key: https://console.anthropic.com/
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ── OpenRouter Adapter ──
# Enables: intent-os run <manifest> --adapter openrouter
# Routes to 200+ models through one API
# Get key: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...

# ── GitHub Models Adapter ──
# Enables: intent-os run <manifest> --adapter github-models
# Free tier for GPT-4o-mini and other models
# Get token: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...

# ── Ollama (Local) ──
# No API key needed. Requires: ollama serve
# Download: https://ollama.com/download
# Pull a model: ollama pull llama3.2:1b
